com.loveboyuan.smarttrader

Class DrawerListEntry

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.loveboyuan.smarttrader.DrawerListEntry

  • public class DrawerListEntry
extends java.lang.Object
    Created by jiahui on 11/29/15. DrawerListEntry is a model that contains information coming from "list_entry" or "list_header_entry" xml waiting to be actually inflated by the DrawerListAdapter model.
